title: Mushrooms 1st MeMe Contest
body:
This contest started on April 13th and complete at April 16th:
https://twitter.com/MushroomsFinan1/status/1381802279255166981

We are glad to see a lot of creative works in our community. It is really fascinating to have all the support from you.

Please VOTE for the candidate which you love most. Note you could vote ONLY once for one candidate. We will sort the voting after end date and pick the final Top5 winners.

You could vote as long as you have MM token in:
- your own wallet like MetaMask
- staking in SuperMario pool
- MM-USDC LP and staked in Mushrooms farming pool 
- MM-ETH SLP and staked in Mushrooms farming pool 
- MM-KP3R SLP and staked in Mushrooms farming pool
